      ◄=============►
       TV Show Notes 
      ◄=============►-----------------------------------------------------►
                                   
       Into The Brain. Series 1, episode 1.

       Documentary series looking at the brutal, bloody and dangerous 
       history of surgery begins with the area of the body where it has 
       been most frightening - the brain. Just over 100 years ago, 
       cutting into the brain was a terrifying prospect for both patient
       and surgeon. From freak accidents involving crowbars through the 
       skull to notorious lobotomies with icepicks, this programme reveals
       how, through mishap and misadventure, brain surgery has become the
       life-saving discipline it is today.

